thout ansible-lint/ansible-playbook installed — this is expected harness behavior\n- All shellcheck checks pass\n- The script follows the exact same patterns as docker-agent and gha-agent\n- FMT_MODE handling follows go-agent conventions\n","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null}}
